&lt;p&gt;36 keys should be enough for everyone&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/6046171639079035614.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-182998/images/6046171639079035614.jpg" src="projects/project-182998/images/6046171639079035614.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
